OL,3,CRussell Brand pleads not guilty to two
OL,4,Cfurther sex offences including rape
OL,6,FComedian and actor Russell Brand has
OL,7,Fpleaded not guilty to two further
OL,8,Fsexual offences, including rape.
OL,10,FBrand previously denied two counts of
OL,11,Frape, one count of indecent assault
OL,12,Fand two counts of sexual assault in
OL,13,Frelation to alleged offences between
OL,14,F1999 and 2005, involving four women.
OL,16,FOn Tuesday at Southwark Crown Court,
OL,17,Fthe 50-year-old pleaded not guilty to
OL,18,Fone further count of rape and one of
OL,19,Fsexual assault, which are both alleged
OL,20,Fto have taken place in 2009.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
