OL,3,CRussell Brand pleads not guilty to two
OL,4,Cfurther sex offences including rape
OL,6,FWearing an animal-print shirt with
OL,7,Fseveral buttons undone and holding a
OL,8,Fwhite hat, Brand spoke from the dock
OL,9,Fto confirm his name and his not-guilty
OL,10,Fpleas.
OL,12,FThe two latest charges relate to two
OL,13,Ffurther women and are alleged to have
OL,14,Ftaken place in London.
