OL,3,CRussell Brand pleads not guilty to two
OL,4,Cfurther sex offences including rape
OL,6,FThe other charge of the original five
OL,7,Falleges the actor indecently assaulted
OL,8,Fanother woman after grabbing her
OL,9,Fforearm and attempting to drag her
OL,10,Finto a male toilet.
OL,12,FBrand, who carried a copy of the Bible
OL,13,Finto the court building before his
OL,14,Fhearing, is due to face trial in June.
OL,16,FHe was charged following an
OL,17,Finvestigation by Channel 4 and The
OL,18,FSunday Times in which several women
OL,19,Fmade allegations against him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
